*Lakše* je uhvatiti ribu u mrežu nego štapom. (It is easier to catch a fish in a net than with a rod.)

*Lakše* je biti bogat nego biti siromašan. (It is easier to be rich than to be poor.)

*Lakše* je izbaciti naviku nego naučiti novu. (It is easier to get rid of a habit than to learn a new one.)

*Lakše* je reći nego učiniti. (It is easier said than done.)

*Lakše* je bilo otići nego ostati. (It was easier to go than to stay.)